message.content: cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE. The paper discusses a method of generating synthetic question answering corpora using models of question generation and answer extraction, which falls under the sub-categories of natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions improvements on SQuAD2 and NQ, which are datasets used for information retrieval (cs.IR) and neural networks (cs.NE).
